    <p>Thank you for your interest in Ryerson University's graduate program in Physics. Below are the general admission requirements. Note that our graduate program is competitive, and it's not possible to offer admission to all who meet the minimum entrance requirements. However, we encourage you to apply, explore our <a href="/content/ryerson/physics/graduate-studies/fields-of-study.html">research fields</a> and <a href="/content/ryerson/physics/our-people.html">potential supervisors</a>, and learn how the admission process works.</p>
    





