<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="1d4e77c4-06c4-4f1d-bde1-ec9ddb61ad30" >

    <p>Candidates may be admitted from various undergraduate programs (e.g. physics, biology, engineering, chemistry, math). Students lacking the necessary background in specific fields may need to complete additional courses.<br> </p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Completion of a four-year undergraduate (or equivalent) degree from an accredited institution</li> 
 <li>Minimum grade point average (GPA) or equivalent of 3.33/4.33 (B+) in the last two years of study</li> 
 <li>Statement of interest</li> 
 <li>Resumé/CV</li> 
 <li>Transcripts</li> 
 <li>Two letters of recommendation</li> 
 <li><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/graduate/future-students/apply/requirements/">English language proficiency</a>, if required (if previous post-secondary program was not conducted in English)<br> </li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
